Legal.privacyBody:
We process personal data (name, phone, email, stay dates) only to handle booking requests and perform the contract, in line with applicable data protection rules.

Protection:
• contact fields in bookings are stored encrypted (AES-256-GCM);
• admin access is role-based;
• admin passwords are stored as secure hashes;
• HTTPS is required in production.

Artificial intelligence:
• personal data is never sent to AI generation services;
• briefs and commercial proposals are generated from depersonalised context only (property, dates, terms);
• name, phone, and email are inserted into the final document on our server after generation.

Cookies may be used for core site features and analytics when enabled. You may request deletion or a copy of your data — see Contacts for how to reach us.
